data.description:
Welcome to this updated, all brick charmer! Perfectly situated on an oversized corner lot with a newly fenced in backyard. This home has been lovingly, well-maintained by its current owners for the last 21 years. Numerous big ticket items have been done with high efficiency in mind including: Newer roof, windows, zoned HVAC system with 98% variable speed/UV light/humidifier, ductwork, hot water heater, PVC plumbing throughout, insulation in walls/roof and all new bathroom with heated towel rack. All electrical has been redone inside and out and all lights are LED. Fresh epoxy in the dry, waterproofed basement with lots of built in storage shelving. Hickory hardwoods and custom tilework. New siding on the fully insulated garage with new heater. This will be a maintenance free home for decades to come!

2 bedrooms upstairs and 2 non-conforming bedrooms downstairs (only missing the egress). Custom tilework and hardwoods throughout. And a special bonus! There's a batting cage/pitching machine in the back that can stay or go. How fun! New countertops and kitchen sink are on order and will be installed soon. These recent empty nesters are excited for their next chapter and ready to welcome YOU to your new home!

Information provided by homeowner and public records.
